#: ../../6-Good dfc29906c00440eaa0dad4f6fdbaa991 practices.rst:15
msgid ""
"While it is clear that a large number of languages in the world require "
"intensive investment in resource creation for technology enablement, it "
"seems highly unlikely that such an investment can be delivered readily "
"and easily in a short span of time. Given these limited resources, "
"language communities should be empowered to determine the future of their"
" languages. In this document, we have presented how digital "
"representation is part of this process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 776e64577e6a4db3803463b3d88955f6 practices.rst:17
msgid ""
"For deciding where to start, we suggest adopting the methodology of 4-D "
"design thinking of *Discover, Design, Develop and Deploy* as introduced "
"by Bali et al. in their `ELLORA initiative <https://www.microsoft.com/en-"
"us/research/project/ellora/>`_. This user-centric approach is as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good aa65d8abe96f4a38a30b6c3f37f0f836 practices.rst:19
msgid "Discover what is most needed by the language community,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 5c1474a92713439f9d78c25a845f70d2 practices.rst:20
msgid ""
"Design for the users and their language giving attention to diversity of "
"the language and avoiding an approach parting from a majority language,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 58bb32c5e6134952aa0da2d181765a77 practices.rst:21
msgid ""
"Develop and deploy frequently in an interative manner constantly "
"improving and detecting failures from the beginning."
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good a2e550d0079744c5a133719bd6e6b966 practices.rst:23
msgid ""
"Even when the community hasn't developed a perspective of language "
"technology development, it is good practice to keep the value of data in "
"mind when doing language preservation activities. Some examples of these "
"are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 54035d66f69a4ac485e7f35e266bbe62 practices.rst:25
msgid ""
"Organize events and create content to raise data-awareness in the "
"language community,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good ee0d060e461d4913942dd205c1656daa practices.rst:26
msgid "Introduce languages to crowdsourcing platforms,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good cef2c71b2c194955ab7bc6b92c50d33e practices.rst:27
msgid "Organize datathons for language data collection,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 1d1ec49fc7ef4c11849f460b8a4e6609 practices.rst:28
msgid "Translate folk tales and children's stories which reside in public domain,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 17fbc2633dd44ec79ef0c6e31b0cc284 practices.rst:29
msgid ""
"Store plain text or document versions of published material in order to "
"create text corpora,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 812dbbabae1342c0b2903d5f71d0d558 practices.rst:30
msgid ""
"Save and openly share translation memories for helping other translators "
"and for creating parallel data,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../6-Good 0afc67b81cdb420985294f6e2a09f747 practices.rst:31
msgid ""
"Store recordings of broadcast material (e.g. radioshows) and transcribe "
"if possible so that they can be converted into speech data,"
msgstr ""

